title: Murder She Solved - Season 1
description:
Murder She Solved - Season 1

Murder She Solved: True Crime, an eight-episode, one hour documentary series, tells the true stories of female crime solvers who, against all odds, have solved some of the most daunting murder cases in North America and Canada. Combining elements of mystery and intrigue, the series' unique visual style and riveting storytelling compels viewers to connect the dots as crime-solvers unravel the clues in their journey to solve the crime.


Ep 1 - Free To Kill
Ep 2 - A Killer Family
Ep 3 - The Pathway Predator
Ep 4 - Murder At The Roadhouse
Ep 5 - Deadly Deception
Ep 6 - On The Trail Of A Hitman
Ep 7 - A Fatal Fare
Ep 8 - Severed
